messages.textToSpeech: We’re going to make music using your voice commands. To add a track to your mix, say something like “Ok Google, add a funky beat” or “Hey Google, give me a happy guitar.” Feel free to hit me up for suggestions at any time.  If you’re ready, let’s start jamming.
messages.displayText: We’re going to make music using your voice commands. To add a track to your mix, say something like “Ok Google, add a funky beat” or “Hey Google, give me a happy guitar.” Feel free to hit me up for suggestions at any time.  If you’re ready, let’s start jamming.
